      "content": "that's a good start. can you make it a bit more specific though? like, really lean into the contrast between the \"chaos\" of the people there and the \"superiority\" of the explorer's culture. maybe have him talk about how they lack basic structures like law or proper religion compared to europe. it needs to feel like he really believes they are inherently incapable of ruling themselves.",
